divs: Sighting DetailsI was on the roof watching the stars,observed an object that seemed to be square...then a triangle with TINY LIGHTS FLASHING,red,brown,black and sort of a creamy yellow-ish light.I followed the object in my sights for a while...for about 2 minutes 2sec,it then appeared to shoot straight up. I looked at the time it was 11:51pm on that tuesday evening.A few hours later at about 2:16am I saw another object move slower at a much higher altitude.
Summary: A slow object that changed shape, with tiny lights flashing.
